      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/crown-castle-beats-site-rental-revenue-estimates-steady-demand-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[無線塔營運商 Crown Castle 週三第一季站點租賃收入超出了華爾街預期，這得益於對其無線基礎設施服務的穩定需求。]]></description>
